reviewText: I should have sent it back but did not bother. I watched it but did not find it to my liking.  It is like an aerobic video.

I have just started using aerobic DVDs to work out at home. I found that this one added new steps too quickly, and spent a lot of time just moving back and forth trying to figure out the move.

Additionally, the women in the aerobics work out were panting hard after the first 2 minutes. I tried to put more energy, and still was barely breathing hard after 5 minutes.

Out of the three DVDs that I purchased, this one gets a thumbs down.
I would recommend and use this seller again. The item was received in good condition and exactly as it was described, in a timely manner. Thank you!
